measurements.description: A striking, well-balanced 3.8-m by 1.5-m multilevel three-sided display up to 2-m high with many ribbon trophy and AOS award winners, a wide variety of genera including Masevallia, Cymbidium, Cattelya, Dendrobium, Paphiopedilum and Coelogyne, both species and hybrids, leading the eye toward the focal point, a large specimen of Coelogyne tenella.
